{"id":179133,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/谁来唤醒教育部留学服务中心的责任与良知？/","date":"2011-09-14T12:31:25Z","modified":"2011-09-14T14:49:17Z","title":"谁来唤醒教育部留学服务中心的责任与良知？","content":"<p><span style=\"color: #464646; font-family: simsun; line-height: 21px; background-color: #bcd3e5;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span><strong>谁来唤醒教育部留学服务中心的责任与良知？</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">继上周发布博文《教育部留学服务中心在大骗局中究竟扮演了什么角色？》、《教育部留学服务中心与北清创意园大骗局》和《教育部留学服务中心现身春晖公司北清创意园大骗局》，三问教育部留学服务中心后，广大博友反应热烈，强烈呼吁追究真相，但可悲的是，教育部留学服务中心漠视民众呼声，三缄其口。一个政府部门，涉嫌假合同联手欺诈政府和消费者，面对质疑之声，竟能泰然处之，不管不顾，是谁给了教育部留学服务中心这样的底气，谁又能唤醒教育部留学服务中心的责任与良知？</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">最新爆料：下图为教育部留学服务中心与春晖公司签署的阴阳协议的截图。<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日签署的协议是骗取土地审批的必要条件，也是骗局的第一个重要节点。可以说，没有这份协议，就不可能获得中关村生民科学园的审批环节。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">下图中代表教育部留学服务中心签字的是邵巍，时任教育部留学服务中心副主任。但<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">24</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日，教育部留学服务中心投资处处长戴争鸣及中心办公室副主任黄立琼曾到生命园公司，证实教育部留学服务中心从未与春晖公司签署、也从未见过签署日期为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日、签署人为邵巍的《合作共建“春晖留学人员创新创业孵化基地”协议书》。教育部留学服务中心投资处处长戴争鸣并在该份协议写下了“此协议不是教育部留学服务中心与北京春晖世纪置业有限公司签署的协议。 戴争鸣 </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2011.5.31</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">”。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">这就证明春晖公司<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月向生命园提交的其与教育部留学服务中心签署的用于证明春晖项目系留学人员创新创业孵化基地的《合作共建协议》是伪造的。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">在有关机构调查此骗局的过程中，教育部留学服务中心一直拒绝出示与春晖公司的《合作共建协议》原件至今。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> 下图是教育部留学服务中心投资处处长戴争鸣确认的签署日期为<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">15</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日的《合作共建协议》，但更加荒诞的是，戴争鸣处长言之凿凿的这份所谓真协议，竟是说要和春晖公司在北京海淀区建设留学人员创新创业孵化基地，而地球人都知道，春晖公司开发的孵化基地在昌平区北清路！由此推想，戴争鸣代表教育部留学服务中心签署的这份真协议的目的是什么？是掩盖罪责，还是继续欺骗政府和消费者？</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21.75pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21.75pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><a href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=8bccef650100wgwd&amp;url=http://s12.sinaimg.cn/orignal/8bccef65gacd18e67751b\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/110.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-179139\" title=\"1\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/110.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"554\" height=\"431\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/110.jpg 554w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/110-300x233.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 554px) 100vw, 554px\" /></a><br />\n</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21.75pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21.75pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/210.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-179140\" title=\"2\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/210.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"554\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/210.jpg 554w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/210-300x210.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 554px) 100vw, 554px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21.75pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/38.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-179141\" title=\"3\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/38.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"554\" height=\"379\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/38.jpg 554w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/38-300x205.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 554px) 100vw, 554px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21.75pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> 从不断变换的说法，驴唇不对马嘴的协议，基本可以推断，教育部留学服务中心投资处处长戴争鸣与春晖公司大骗局有直接关系，部分或全部参与了骗局的设计和实施。戴争鸣啊，真是太有创意了，太有才了！弥天大谎，你都不眨眼睛！</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">从现有的证据链看，教育部留学服务中心与春晖公司项目（北清创意园）大骗局有纠缠不清的干系，要么利用手中权力，利益输送，要么合伙诈骗，是利益共同体。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">从大骗局被多次揭露并不了了之，可以判断，教育部留学服务中心主任白章德等负有不可推卸的失察、包庇甚至参与骗局的责任。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">教育部留学服务中心承办的“春晖杯”留学人员创业创新大赛，与春晖公司究竟有什么利益关系？</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">请各位网友协助清查，教育部留学服务中心是否还用此类手法在全国各地招摇撞骗，继续作恶？</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">请负有正义感的网友支持揭黑行动，唤醒教育部留学服务中心的责任与良知！大家一起喊，教育部留学服务中心白章德、邵巍、戴争鸣，你妈喊你出来说清问题！</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> 人物链接一：教育部留学服务中心主任白章德</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><a href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=8bccef650100wgwd&amp;url=http://s3.sinaimg.cn/orignal/8bccef65gacd199d03a02\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/41.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-179142\" title=\"4\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/41.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"554\" height=\"509\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/41.jpg 554w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/41-300x275.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 554px) 100vw, 554px\" /></a><br />\n</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">人物链接二：教育部留学服务中心副主任邵巍</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/51.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-179144\" title=\"5\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/51.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"554\" height=\"447\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/51.jpg 554w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/51-300x242.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 554px) 100vw, 554px\" /></a><br />\n</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> 人物链接三：教育部留学服务中心投资处处长戴争鸣</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><a href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=8bccef650100wgwd&amp;url=http://s14.sinaimg.cn/orignal/8bccef65gacd1af17efbd\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/61.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-179145\" title=\"6\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/61.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"554\" height=\"532\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/61.jpg 554w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/09/61-300x288.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 554px) 100vw, 554px\" /></a><br />\n</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 21pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;\">\n<p></span></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[20534],"tags":[9364,10464,11706,10586]}